<br>
Lastly, on a blue server you also have PnP. PnP will still apply on your server, even in a guildwar. You zone in on Guild X doing Rallos Zek and dispel/dot all the CC'd mobs so they break mez, summon and cause the raid to wipe.<br>
<br>
Now you are getting petitioned and possibly banned, even though you really didn't do anything illegal.<br>
