<br>
If you go red on a blue server you can only attack other people that are also red and you basicaly can't group ir interact or be healed or get buffs from blue players.<br>
<br>
The biggest reason PvP will never fly with most people is griefers.  There are two many idiots and jerks out there that many would rather not deal with even if it means they will never have the ocasional fun PvP encounter.  I would love to have a little PvP action and be able to come accross a group of troll players and have my Erudite try and reason with them before getting eaten to add spice to things.  But I would much rather NEVER ever ever ever ever have to face a stupid greifer.  The other problem with PvP (and role playing) is too many people are shoot first ask questions latter.<br>
<br>
Untail the gaming industry finds a way to penalize and kill off imature greifers without killing off the players that might make a mistake, PvP is not the way to go. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=reynorfyrestalker>Reynor Fyrestalker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br>  Posts: 322<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/18/03 1:28:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25419.topic&index=25>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.luclin.org/files/reynor/dnce45.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Blue Server PvP Thought for discussion</span><hr size=1> if you really like PvP try DAoC <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=90927"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.luclin.org/files/reynor/sig_5.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vaged>Vaged</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#ffffff>(3/18/03 2:56:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25419.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Blue Server PvP Thought for discussion</span><hr size=1> During and after reading this thread I laughed. Thanks.<br>
