<br>
Query though: Does Concussion work in PvP?<br>
<br>
Because it seems to me that it could. Here's how: A successful concussion would remove the current target / force the player to retarget. Alternately, a successful concusion could switch the enemy players target to himself, forcing a manual retarget, or worse.<br>
<br>
Minor? Yeah maybe. But I can think of a few scenarios where that might be a fun trick with real application in PvP, while remaining in - line with the concept / intent of the spell.<br>
